RS-MSPs in Procedure CreatingRemove (Fig. 6). 3) There are sr S-MSPs in G5s√∞A; B√û that correspond to CRS-MSPs in the unsigned breakpoint graph and are transformed into
RS-MSPs. The sr S-MSPs are removed in step 6 of the cycle
